{%- comment -%}
  Button Component
  Description: A reusable button component with optional icon.
  Accepts:
  - button_text: Text to display on button (default: 'Click here')
  - button_style: Style variant of button (default: 'black') 
  - icon_size: Size of icon in pixels (default: '25px')
  - icon_url: URL of icon image (default: 'icon_arrow_right.svg')
  - button_onclick: onClick handler (default: 'false')
{%- endcomment -%}
